  "prompt": "Where can I find a free online course to learn WordPress themes management?",
  "response": "There are several platforms where you can find free online courses to learn about WordPress theme management. Here are some recommendations:\n\n1. **Coursera**: Offers free courses on WordPress, including themes and customization. Look for courses that allow you to audit for free.\n\n2. **edX**: Similar to Coursera, you can find courses related to WordPress. Many courses are free to audit.\n\n3. **Udemy**: While many courses cost money, there are also free courses available. Search for \"free WordPress themes management\" to find them.\n\n4. **YouTube**: There are countless tutorials and guides on WordPress theme management. Channels focused on web development often have comprehensive playlists.\n\n5. **WPBeginner**: This website offers various tutorials and guides on using WordPress, including themes. They have a wealth of information suitable for beginners.\n\n6. **WordPress.org**: The official WordPress website has documentation and tutorials that can help you understand theme management.\n\n7. **Khan Academy**: While not specifically focused on WordPress, they do offer some courses in web development that might be useful.\n\nRemember to check for reviews and ratings on any course you consider to ensure that it's reputable and well-informed. Happy learning!",
